title: HKG Chief Exec Carrie Lam visits Thailand
description:
(4 Aug 2017) Hong Kong's Chief Executive Carrie Lam met with Thai Prime Minister Prayuth Chan-ocha in Bangkok on Friday. 
It was Lam's first visit to Thailand since she took office in July this year.  
The two sides are expected to discuss cooperation on industry, economy and tourism and support for Thailand's Eastern Economic Corridor initiative. 
Before her trip, Lam visited Singapore as part of her effort to bring closer ties between Hong Kong and ASEAN countries.
